First, install pktanon

Next create a profile for the capture you want to do

Usage with two example profiles.
Can extend anonymization using manual, update xml file:
http://www.tm.uka.de/software/pktanon/documentation/manual/pdf/PktAnon_Manual.pdf

Reading from File:

tcpdump -i <interface name> -w <pcap name>

Specify <pcap name> in the xml file as Input File
Specify <output file> in the xml file as Output File

pktanon from_capture.xml

Live Capture

tcpdump -i <interface name> -w - | pktanon live_capture.xml

